{"tid":1498631,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[恐怖]一人藍冚家藍","createTime":"2019-08-23T13:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T17:17:51.000Z","uid":260895,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"854d7f9000945f1e40419b2491a3136ee30a778f","tid":1498631,"uid":260895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:01:08.000Z","msg":"講起就嬲，岩岩同家姐嘈完交。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：示威者好暴力喎！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：築人鏈都暴力？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：而家無啫，夜啲就有。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：就算有衝突都主要係針對黑警。<br />\n<br />\n佢聽到黑警兩個字突然燥底<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：機場係咪你班示威者攪事呀？塞紅隧係咪你地攪事先呀？！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我地承認有錯，已經道埋歉。咁邊個射咁多催淚彈呀？邊個打無辜嘅市民呀？<br />\n<br />\n老竇老母叫我地唔好嘈，佢開始理虧，然後好大聲咁話......<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你地班人根本係歪理，暴力，暴徒！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你係咪撐警撐到傻撚咗？仲話係大學生，良知都無埋呀你！<br />\n<br />\n老竇老母再次勸交。佢焗到塊面紅撚晒，然後飯都唔食就走撚咗。<br />\n<br />\n事源：佢嫁咗俾一個細佬做警察嘅人，佢細佬近兩年入警隊，佢老公本身黃，佢本身都黃，然後兩年後冚家變藍。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b73b8c694619fe52de06e8c3c675a5354e01fa2","tid":1498631,"uid":260895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:01:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"edad93bdd60cb437c6b82e49bea597b1baef6af9","tid":1498631,"uid":260895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:02:10.000Z","msg":"嬲撚到我"},{"pid":"bf589999a626619315b378f3f9017d44f2fafc5b","tid":1498631,"uid":260895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:02:27.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5da059bfe80c9a4c3e68b9016dd6007755d378e4","tid":1498631,"uid":260895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:02:38.000Z","msg":"再自推"},{"pid":"2bbdf400d596f311e64dc105b256265f5ccfacd3","tid":1498631,"uid":260895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:02:48.000Z","msg":"再再自推"},{"pid":"f7c65cba7a6ad9f5dfd4b35a7f4988461d4f87ce","tid":1498631,"uid":260895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:03:12.000Z","msg":"點解啲人咁易變藍絲"},{"pid":"c39dd71ef5b189490993f944b04de5e785e5369e","tid":1498631,"uid":260895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:03:25.000Z","msg":"皇天擊殺"},{"pid":"f7db0bf1ed670df5b148751c5048364030f56cc3","tid":1498631,"uid":260895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:03:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a617160bbc641dea3326e1497b7c0c4c97c115c6","tid":1498631,"uid":260895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:03:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0c5bc5ad5bfa4055cd21c28ac5825857152141f","tid":1498631,"uid":260895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:04:04.000Z","msg":"我再推"},{"pid":"ba0e113eafbfe19e491a146033733938b388609f","tid":1498631,"uid":260895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:04:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d4b5ccd15a954e88a6898d493c879958c86db74","tid":1498631,"uid":260895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:05:24.000Z","msg":"嬲呀"},{"pid":"f493f098f745593a0dd25882b0c9a5cf20216f5b","tid":1498631,"uid":260895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:07:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c6abab6732e38d4be050342570e6b7d7d29a0d8","tid":1498631,"uid":180975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7c65cba7a6ad9f5dfd4b35a7f4988461d4f87ce","tid":1498631,"uid":260895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08